{
  "chapter": 1,
  "chapter_summary": "第一回：情人的手\n\n风四娘在乱石山强盗窝洗澡时，被解老二等七八个强盗偷看。她用银针刺瞎了众人的眼睛，随后花平出现，一刀杀死了所有强盗。风四娘与花平是老朋友，花平曾是关中群盗之首，以快刀名动江湖。风四娘此行入关是想找萧十一郎帮忙，但花平告诉她，萧十一郎砍断了他的左臂，刀法天下第一。风四娘不愿承认对萧十一郎的感情，转而去找飞大夫公孙铃。公孙铃是武林名医，轻功高绝，指功天下第一，医道高绝，人称公孙三绝。风四娘找到公孙铃时，他不在家，只有应门童子。风四娘在路口等待时，看到两个轿夫抬着一个老人，突然轿夫拔剑刺向老人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位难道从来没有看过女人洗澡吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我不但看过女人洗澡，替女人洗澡更是我的拿手本事，你要不要我替你擦擦背？包你满意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_huo_zi",
      "text": "我背上正痒得很呢！你既然愿意，就快进来吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_huo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "小伙子",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "解老二，你已经有好几个老婆了，何必再跟我抢这趟生意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你擦背若也像打人这么重，我可受不了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知道这是什么地方？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "我若不知道，怎么会来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "这里是乱石山，又叫做强盗山，因为住在山上的人都是强盗，就连这小客栈的老板看来虽很老实，其实也是强盗。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你既然知道这是什么地方，居然还敢来？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "我又不是来惹你们的，只不过想来洗个澡而已，有什么关系呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你什么地方不好洗，偏偏要到这里来洗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "也许我就喜欢强盗看我洗澡呢，这岂非很刺激？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "幸好我没叫这人来替我擦背，粗手粗脚的……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "光棍眼里不揉沙子，你究竟是为什么来的？还不老实说出来？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你倒真没有猜错，我千里迢迢赶到这里来，自然不会只为了要洗个澡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是不是有人派你来刺探这里的消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "那倒没有，我只不过想来看个老朋友而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "但这里并没有你的朋友！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你怎么知道没有，难道我就不能跟强盗交朋友？说不定我也是强盗呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你的朋友是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "我也有很久没见过他了，听说他这几年混得很不错，已当了关中群盗的老大哥，不知你认不认得他？",
      "tone": "悠然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "关中黑道上的朋友有十三帮，每帮都有个老大哥，不知你说的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "他好像已当了你们十三帮强盗的总瓢把子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "就凭你这女人，也配跟我们的总瓢把子交朋友？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "我为什么不能跟他交朋友？你可知道我是谁么？",
      "tone": "嫣然",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你是谁？你难道还会是风四娘那个女妖怪不成？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你是不是'两头蛇'解不得？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不错，无论谁见到我这两头蛇都得死，谁也解不得！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你既然是两头蛇，我就只好是风四娘了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们偷看了女人洗澡，难道就想这样随随便便的走了吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你……你想怎样？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你难道还想让我们看得更清楚些不成？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "哦——原来你是欺负我没有穿衣服，不敢跳起来追你们？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不错，除非你洗澡时也带着家伙，坐在洗澡盆里也能杀人。",
      "tone": "怪笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "你们看，我这只手像是杀人的手吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "speaker_name": "解老二",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_jie_lao_er",
      "text": "我看也不像，奇怪的是，有时它偏偏会杀人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "偷看女人洗澡，会长'针眼'的。这句话你们难道没听见过？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好好的一双手，不用来绣花，却用来杀人，真是可惜得很……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "花平？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我就知道是你来了！除了你之外，还有谁能在一瞬间就杀死七个人！还有谁能使这么快的刀！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我知道你杀他们，是为了要让他们少受痛苦，却不知你的心几时也变得如此软了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是风四娘？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "难得你还听得出我的声音，还没有忘了我。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "除了风四娘外，世上还有谁在洗澡时也带着暗青子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "原来你也在偷看我洗澡，否则你怎会知道我在洗澡的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "你要看，为什么不大大方方的进来看呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你出关六七年，大家都觉得很太平，你为什么又回来了呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "因为我想你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "你不相信我想你？我若不想你，为什么来找你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "你为什么要叹气？你以为我来找你一定没有好事？一个人发达了，连老朋友的面都不想见了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你穿上衣裳，我等会见你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我已经穿上衣服了，你进来吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "有人存心想来偷看我洗澡，我就要杀了他，你存心不想看，我倒反而偏要让你瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "听说你前几年杀了'太原一剑'高飞，是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "听说'太行双刀'丁家兄弟也是败在你刀下的，是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "高飞和丁家兄弟都是武林中一等一的高手，你居然能将他们杀了，可见你的刀法已越来越快了。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我这次入关，就为的是要看看你的快刀！",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你真的要看？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "你也用不着紧张，我不是来找你比划的，因为我既不愿死在你的刀下，也舍不得杀你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那你就不必看了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为我的刀只是用来杀人的，不是给人看的！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我若偏偏要看呢？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好，你就看吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "我想看的是你杀人的刀法，不是劈柴的刀法，在老朋友面前，你又何苦还要藏私呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "藏私？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "你的刀法虽然是左右开弓，出手双飞，但江湖中谁不知道你用的是左手刀？你的左手至少比右手快一倍。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你一定要看我的左手刀？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "看定了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好，你看吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "这……这难道是被人砍断的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "对方用的是剑？还是斧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是刀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "刀？还有谁的刀比你更快？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只有一个人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "这人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎，萧十一郎……你总该认得他的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "不错，我认得他……我当然认得他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你想不想找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "谁说我要找他？我为什么要找他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你迟早总是要找他的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "放你的屁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "其实用不着骗我，我早知道你这次入关是为了要做一件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "谁说的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我虽不知道你要做的是什么事，但却知道那必定是一件大事，你生怕自己一个人的力量不够，想找个帮手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以你才会来找我，只可惜你找错人了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "就算你猜的不错，我还是可以去找别人，为什么一定要找萧十一郎？武林中的高手难道都死光了吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "但除了他之外，还有谁能帮你的忙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "谁说没有，我现在就去找个人给你瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ping",
      "speaker_name": "花平",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你想去找谁？莫非是飞大夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "不错，我正是找他！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_hua_ping",
      "text": "飞大夫有哪点比不上萧十一郎？他不但轻功高绝，指上的那份功夫，十个萧十一郎加起来只怕也比不上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_ying_men_tong_zi",
      "text": "公孙先生在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_ying_men_tong_zi",
      "text": "公孙先生哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_ying_men_tong_zi",
      "text": "公孙先生今天回不回来？什么时候回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ying_men_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "应门童子",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_mian_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "前面的轿夫",
      "listener": "char_hou_mian_jiao_fu",
      "text": "前面好长的一段山路，咱们在这里歇歇脚再往上爬吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_mian_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "后面的轿夫",
      "listener": "char_qian_mian_jiao_fu",
      "text": "这两天我精神不继，上山时咱们换个边吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_mian_jiao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "前面的轿夫",
      "listener": "char_hou_mian_jiao_fu",
      "text": "好小子，又想偷懒，莫非昨晚上又去报效了小甜瓜两次，我看你迟早总有一天死在她肚子上。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 1,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    }
